Bomber will be:
        Dedicated to involving Jenn in stuff I enjoy; coding and gaming
        A bomberman clone
        Multi platform
        Event based
        Multiplayer (local, network later)
        Flexible as far as clients go
        A way for me to learn more python
        
Status:
        Turn based game engine working to Alpha level

Plan:
        Move to event-based
        Move to time-based, bombs tick down over 3 seconds
        GUI interface (Linux/Windows/Mac)
        Networking (Client/Server)
        Consider Stackless for Server
        Console interface for POSIX (curses)

Potential library choices:
        http://github.com/saucelabs/monocle
        http://www.gevent.org/

